    "attributes": {
        "action": "Create a \u2018Residential Care Voucher\u2019 scheme",
        "additional_details": "A scheme should exist where:\r\nEmployees can pay into a \u2018pot\u2019 that is dedicated to the residential / end-of-life care of loved ones.\r\nMonies saved are protected by a government-backed scheme (similar to savings at the bank)\r\nSavings to the employee are present through salary-sacrifice\r\nMonies deposited  are available should they become not necessary\r\nPeople can chose to pay into their own account and/or an account for a relative/friend \r\n\r\nThe scheme should mirror the current childcare voucher scheme",
        "background": "As a parent to a young child, I can take advantage of the tax-efficient way to pay towards her childcare. I propose a similar scheme be set up so that people can save towards the often unmanageable costs surrounding residential care for elderly loved ones.",
